  "body": "#### Overview of the Issue\r\n\r\nMake keyspace `db1`\r\n\r\nNeed to fix query:\r\n`show tables where Tables_in_db1 = 'products'`\r\n\r\nThis works:\r\n`show tables where Tables_in_vt_db1 = 'products'`\r\n\r\nLooks like we're using the underlying db name, and not the keyspace name.\r\n\r\n`go-gorm` is a Golang ORM that relies on this behavior to inspect the database:\r\nhttps://github.com/jinzhu/gorm/blob/master/dialect_mysql.go#L176\r\n\r\nPresumably `show indexes` and `show columns` has the same problem.",
